precis:
Amendments to the WESTERN GRAIN TRANSITION PAYMENTS REGULATIONS which
extend the deadline for the acceptance of applications to February 29,
1996, amend the distance factors used to calculate payments and allow the
Minister to accept information pertinent to the application from the
landowner.
